title: Fox MTB Presents | Unmistakable Confidence | Spring '15 Freeride Collection
description:
Spring ’15 Freeride Collection with Brett Rheeder, Cam McCaul, Tyler McCaul, Kyle Strait and Kenny Smith. We got some great footage of our Freeride team from our spring ’15 shoot. It's always fun doing an edit when you have a team like this: Brett Rheeder, Cam McCaul, Tyler
McCaul, Kyle Strait and Kenny Smith. The guys absolutely crushed it on this edit. 

Video by Rootone

Sun Gods In Exile
"Smoke and Fire"
Thanks For The Silver
